==历史==
流行文化中切·格瓦拉的形象源自摄影作品[[英勇的游擊隊員|英勇的游擊隊員]]。 尚不明确何时开始被时尚设计界所使用，<ref name="Sal">{{Cite web |last = Watkins |first = Valentine |authorlink =  |coauthors =  |title = Cool t-shirt, bro |work = [[Salient_(magazine)|Salient (magazine)]] |location =  |date = May 3, 2010 |url = http://www.salient.org.nz/features/cool-t-shirt-bro |format =  |doi =  |accessdate = November 5, 2010 |archive-date = 2014-09-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140904001244/http://salient.org.nz/features/cool-t-shirt-bro |dead-url = no }}</ref> 只知1967年爱尔兰艺术家Jim Fitzpatrick基于此照片重新创作了一幅海报。<ref>Trisha Ziff, ''Che Guevara: Revolutionary & Icon'', Abrams Image, 2006, pg 21</ref>

== 回应==
切·格瓦拉潮流的大行其道，引起了诸多批评，声称不应忽视他的缺陷，也不应将他的行为浪漫化。 评论认为年轻人像支持偶像一样支持切·格瓦拉，却没有意识到他形象背后的种种争议，比如，他曾被认为支持[[暴力|暴力]]作为实现目标的手段之一，他也曾把[[古巴|古巴]]经济拖入泥潭。<ref name="age" /> 评论者称此潮流为“昙花一现，不足挂齿”。<ref name="SMC">{{Cite web |last = Bowen III |first = DK |authorlink =  |coauthors =  |title = Che Guevara: once a revolutionary, now just a T-shirt fad |publisher = [[The_Collegian_(Stewart's_Melville_College)|The Collegian]] |location =  |date = October 23, 2007 |url = https://www.google.co.in/?gfe_rd=cr&ei=rPDlU67NHYzV8geH3YCYBg&gws_rd=ssl |doi =  |accessdate = November 5, 2010 |archive-date = 2021-04-21 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210421162205/https://www.google.co.in/?gfe_rd=cr&ei=rPDlU67NHYzV8geH3YCYBg&gws_rd=ssl |dead-url = no }}{{date=December 2012}}</ref>

流亡海外的古巴人社区也以同样理由，反对切的形象被用作流行文化。<ref name="CI">{{Cite web |last = Marquez |first = Myriam |authorlink =  |coauthors =  |title = Revolutionist Che Guevara T-Shirts Keep Reality Under Wraps |publisher = [[Clarkson_University|Clarkson University]] |location =  |date = April 4, 2005 |url = http://media.www.clarksonintegrator.com/media/storage/paper280/news/2005/04/04/Opinion/Revolutionist.Che.Guevara.TShirts.Keep.Reality.Under.Wraps-910465.shtml |doi =  |accessdate = November 5, 2010 |archive-date = 2010-08-11 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100811012349/http://media.www.clarksonintegrator.com/media/storage/paper280/news/2005/04/04/Opinion/Revolutionist.Che.Guevara.TShirts.Keep.Reality.Under.Wraps-910465.shtml |dead-url = no }}</ref>

切·格瓦拉的长女阿蕾达·格瓦拉，则对这个从她父亲头像衍生出的潮流趋势表示坚决的支持态度，她说：“穿切·格瓦拉T恤的人，通常是不轻易妥协的人，他们不满足于社会现状，时刻思索着如何才能造福于人类社会。我想，我父亲应该是会赞成这样的事的。”<ref name="Guardian" />

